te-tea-shot-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-ingredients-in-a-white-tea-shot-recipe\"\u003eIngredients in a White Tea Shot Recipe \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVodka\u003c/strong\u003e – Choose your favorite unflavored vodka. I used Tito’s. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePeach Schnapps\u003c/strong\u003e – This gives your shot the most flavor and is an essential ingredient. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSweet and Sour Mix\u003c/strong\u003e – For best flavor, try our \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/make-your-own-sour-mix/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003ehomemade sour mix\u003c/a\u003e. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLemon Lime Soda\u003c/strong\u003e – Such as Sprite, to top. Citrus soda gives the shot a nice fizzy texture and adds some more sweetness.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-is-there-tea-in-a-white-tea-shot\"\u003eIs there tea in a White Tea Shot? \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eSimilarly to the \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/green-tea-shot/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eGreen Tea Shot\u003c/a\u003e, there is no loose leaf tea, or tea of any kind in this sweet shot, which is a spinoff of the green tea shot, named for having the appearance and color of green tea. This shot has a cloudy white color and a fun, fruity flavor.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"960\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/white-tea-shot/?tp_image_id=119810\" data-pin-title=\"white tea shot\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients-300x240.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients-1024x819.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients-768x614.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients-100x80.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients-75x60.jpg 75w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients-750x600.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients-730x584.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients-700x560.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients-550x440.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients-156x125.jpg 156w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%20960\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients-300x240.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients-1024x819.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients-768x614.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients-100x80.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients-75x60.jpg 75w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients-750x600.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients-730x584.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients-700x560.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients-550x440.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients-156x125.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-ingredients.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-directions\"\u003eDirections\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eBegin by mixing equal parts of the vodka, peach schnapps and sweet and sour mix in a cocktail shaker with ice cubes. Use a jigger to measure each ingredient.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eShake for 10-15 seconds. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003ePour into shot glasses, the built-in strainer will strain out the ice. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eTop each shot with a cold splash of lemon-lime soda.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"960\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/white-tea-shot/?tp_image_id=119811\" data-pin-title=\"white tea shot\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe-300x240.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe-1024x819.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe-768x614.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe-100x80.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe-75x60.jpg 75w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe-750x600.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe-730x584.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe-700x560.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe-550x440.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe-156x125.jpg 156w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%20960\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe-300x240.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe-1024x819.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe-768x614.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe-100x80.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe-75x60.jpg 75w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe-750x600.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe-730x584.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe-700x560.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe-550x440.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe-156x125.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-recipe.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-tips-for-making\"\u003eTips for Making\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eGarnish ideas: lime wedge, lemon wedge, orange wedge, fresh mint sprig. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eHave you ever tried \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/make-your-own-sour-mix/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003emaking your own sour mix\u003c/a\u003e? It’s fun and really fresh and tasty. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eIf you don’t have vodka on hand, you can substitute it for white rum, tequila or gin. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eFor a fun flavor variation, try using different vodka flavors.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eFreeze your shot glasses ahead of time for an even colder shot. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eSubstitutions: If you don’t have \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/make-your-own-sour-mix/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003esour mix\u003c/a\u003e on hand, you can sub for \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/simple-syrup-recipe/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003esimple syrup\u003c/a\u003e with either fresh lemon juice or fresh lime juice added. \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-white-tea-shot-variations\"\u003eWhite Tea Shot Variations \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/green-tea-shot/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGreen Tea Shot\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e – Swap vodka for Irish whiskey and you’ve got a classic green tea shot. \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhite Tea Shot with Rum\u003c/strong\u003e – Swap vodka for rum for this variation.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhite Tea Cocktail\u003c/strong\u003e – If you don’t like shots and prefer to sip your drink, you can turn this recipe into a cocktail easily. Just double the recipe and pour it into a cocktail glass instead of a shot glass. \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"960\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/white-tea-shot/?tp_image_id=119812\" data-pin-title=\"white tea shot\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.-.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.-.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.--300x240.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.--1024x819.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.--768x614.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.--100x80.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.--75x60.jpg 75w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.--750x600.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.--730x584.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.--700x560.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.--550x440.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.--156x125.jpg 156w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%20960\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.-.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.--300x240.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.--1024x819.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.--768x614.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.--100x80.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.--75x60.jpg 75w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.--750x600.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.--730x584.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.--700x560.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.--550x440.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.--156x125.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot.-.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-serving-suggestions-goes-great-with\"\u003eServing Suggestions/Goes Great With\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eOther recipes you may like:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/20-easy-party-appetizer-ideas/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003e20 Party Appetizers\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/chocolate-covered-strawberries/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eChocolate Covered Cherries\u003c/a\u003e \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/long-island-iced-tea/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eLong Island Iced Tea\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/birthday-cake-pops/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eBirthday Cake Pops\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/cherry-limeade-recipe/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eCherry Limeade\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/virgin-mojito/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eVirgin Mojito\u003c/a\u003e \u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/boilermaker/\"\u003eBoilermak\u003c/a\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/boilermaker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003eer\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2\u003eFAQ\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch2\u003eFrequently Asked Questions\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1660152942311\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eWhat is the difference between a White Tea Shot and a Green Tea Shot? \u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eA white tea shot uses vodka and a green tea shot uses Jameson Irish whiskey. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1660152944117\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eWhat is a White Tea Shot made of? \u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eA white tea shot is made of vodka, peach schnapps, sweet and sour mix and lemon-lime soda. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1660152945459\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eIs there tea in a White Tea Shot? \u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eThese is no tea in a white tea shot. This recipe is a spinoff of the \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/green-tea-shot/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003egreen tea shot\u003c/a\u003e, which is named for having the appearance of tea, but also contains no actual tea. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003cdetails id=\"faq-question-1700229936401\"\u003e\u003csummary\u003e\u003ch3\u003eDo White Tea Shots taste like alcohol? \u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e \u003cp\u003eThe flavor of vodka is very masked beneath the flavors of peach schnapps, sour mix and lemon-lime soda. I would consider this a sweet shot with minimal alcohol flavor compared to other shots. \u003c/p\u003e \u003c/details\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"960\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/white-tea-shot/?tp_image_id=119813\" data-pin-title=\"white tea shot\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot--300x240.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot--1024x819.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot--768x614.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot--100x80.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot--75x60.jpg 75w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot--750x600.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot--730x584.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot--700x560.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot--550x440.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot--156x125.jpg 156w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%20960\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot--300x240.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot--1024x819.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot--768x614.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot--100x80.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot--75x60.jpg 75w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot--750x600.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot--730x584.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot--700x560.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot--550x440.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot--156x125.jpg 156w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/white-tea-shot-.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv id=\"wprm-recipe-container-120024\" data-recipe-id=\"120024\" data-servings=\"1\"\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"acf-helper-block_c3767ed98ae9141d9b2fd0d0b693ab13\"\u003e\n\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGet our FREE recipe guide with our \u003cem\u003emost popular\u003c/em\u003e recipes of all time!\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"#popup-1\" data-lity=\"\"\u003eGet the Guide\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\n\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003csection\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003ch3\u003eIngredients\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"120024\" data-servings=\"1\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e▢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounce \u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003evodka\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e▢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounce \u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003epeach schnapps\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e▢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eounce \u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003esweet and sour mix \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003clabel for=\"wprm-checkbox-3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e▢ \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/label\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003esplash \u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003elemon-lime soda \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t \n\n\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003e\u003ch3\u003eInstructions\u003c/h3\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"120024\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-120024-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eBegin by mixing equal parts of the vodka, peach schnapps and sweet and sour mix in a cocktail shaker with ice.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-120024-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eShake for 10-15 seconds.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-120024-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePour into shot glasses, straining out the ice.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-120024-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTop each shot with a splash of cold lemon-lime soda.\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e \n\n\t\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eYou will need a cocktail shaker, but if you don’t have one, a mason jar or even a sports water bottle makes a good cocktail shaker in a pinch.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eHave you ever tried \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/make-your-own-sour-mix/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"\u003emaking your own sour mix\u003c/a\u003e? It’s fun and really fresh and tasty.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eIf you don’t have vodka on hand, you can substitute it for white rum, tequila or gin.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFreeze your shot glasses ahead of time for an even colder shot.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\t\n\n\t\t\n\t\t\n\t\t\u003cdetails\u003e\n\n    \u003csummary\u003e\u003c/summary\u003e\n\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cp\u003eNutrition Facts\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhite Tea Shot\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAmount per Serving\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e% Daily Value*\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e* Percent Daily Values are based on a 2000 calorie diet.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eNotice: Nutrition is auto-calculated, using Spoonacular, for your convenience. Where relevant, we recommend using your own nutrition calculations.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/details\u003e\n\n\n\t\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/article\u003e    \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003c/main\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
